Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}早安 今天请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有从经纪人那拿到剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有剧本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为不能写 不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有这种卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想要你抽1张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}抽到的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}上面有写字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}像是指令的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我不要  我不要\N要请你做上面写的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}来 请抽\N真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}哪个最轻松啊?\N不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有轻松的\N这张?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要抽那张吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我不要\N我不会再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}中间好了\N可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这张没问题吗?\N不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请抽\N这张比较好? 可以吗? 那张的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这张？\N不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这张这张可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好 请看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}脸OO...身体在车内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这是什么啊?是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那就是这样 可以退还吗?\N不能退还
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我不要 那现在啊 就那写的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要请JULIA你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吧?\N才不是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等下会说明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天没问题吗?\N才不是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请多指教\N虽不是没问题 但还是请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}偷偷摸摸惊心动魄性爱大作战JULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?\N我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没听说啊那种的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}脸OO是身体在车内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是 就是说啊 脸啊\NOO是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}OO?现在在某车站前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}挺多人经过的能请你打开窗户看一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这是玩真的吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}脸稍微露出的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}来给JULIA你爽一下吧 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不会很可疑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不可疑吧?只要不出声就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那啊要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}脱掉内裤吧\N骗人? 对 内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}能给我脱掉吗?\N真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以吗?\N真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以了吧?这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不 若是现在这状态的话脸也在车内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}身体也在车内不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可是。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}出声会被发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA酱\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}都湿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}为什么这么湿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}露出脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等 会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}会看到胸部的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不忍住声音的话\N可能会忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不忍住的话会被发现哦\N那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为外面有很多人啊\N会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}努力忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA小穴咕啾咕啾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}小穴咕啾咕啾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}兴奋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}难不成啊 不讨厌这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}露出脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要去时跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很湿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么了?快去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要去了 露出脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}流了好多汗 过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不关起来的话会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}小穴咕啾咕啾啊 很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经不需要裙子了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}为什么关起来了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想说已经可以了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}以为已经可以了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}小穴真湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}小穴整个撑开来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}一直在忍耐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}叫那么大声会被听见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}窗户已经关起来了 所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不露出脸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}两边都会在车内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为会忍不住声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA好像....小穴的爱液流下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又去了吗?躺下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}忍不住了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想再去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经不再露脸了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那可以多叫点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}现在什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}终于能叫出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有被看到吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}一直在忍耐啊好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}以为会漏出叫声来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}难不成不讨厌这种的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}做之前是很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能不讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}到了啊JULIA到了啊这里是哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里是那个啊某··
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}的的确是某…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA这个这张卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}刚刚JULIA又抽了啊这张卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}嘛是那么真格的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请JULIA你做的也有点过分是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}之后就那个啊…去了再好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}什么啊?总之走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吧?\N是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那走吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这种状态的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}1日店长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我行吗?\N很好看啊 要做什么好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}第一次来好多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那啊接下来这间店是JULIA的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害 怎么办?\N那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是有很多客人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有客人那…JULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}得啊是来当店长的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在这里想请你对店有贡献\N要怎么做啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}应该是是促进贩卖\N这个如何做?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}能请你去跑业务吗?\N要怎做?我没跑过业务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不知道?光是搭话的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}谁?\N那个人 欧吉桑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}你好在找什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这边。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想要什么颜色啊?\N果然粉红色的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这间店有很多种类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是啊 有很多种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}果然还是粉红色好啊\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有很多种类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我很常来啊\N请慢慢看 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很棒哦\N好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害JULIA怎么办?可以了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}再做一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.78,0:23:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}就那样去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}年轻人比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在找什么啊?\NJULIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:23:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是的 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以的话能握个手吗?\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请加油\N好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.54,0:24:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请慢慢看\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}能见到你很开心\N谢谢 请慢慢看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是JULIA的粉丝吗?\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.77,0:24:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA挺常看的吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}身材很好 胸部又大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.84,0:24:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好害羞\N害羞?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那么机会难得 请买点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.78,0:24:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}知道了 有自慰套吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}知道了 请慢慢看\N请加油 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害\N吓一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.09,0:25:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害\N这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.80,0:25:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}果然会被发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.81,0:25:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}吓了一跳 不会被觉得很怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.57,0:25:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为是1日店
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.74,0:25:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有被觉得很怪吗?\N没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}也有下面\N下面好像也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.75,0:25:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}也去下面好了\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.82,0:25:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能有客人在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.12,0:25:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有很多假屌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.68,0:25:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不亏是JULIA 你都知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.83,0:25:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}也有很多自慰套
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}自慰套 刚那个人在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里…啊JULIA\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里有收银台是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.91,0:25:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}接着请你站收银台吧\N结帐?结帐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.78,0:25:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我很想做啊 我没做过\N真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.79,0:25:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天有拿到店里人的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.86,0:26:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那若有客人来的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.79,0:26:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请你接客\N是 要怎做好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.89,0:26:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请按这里\N可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.80,0:26:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有反应\N没反应?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.82,0:26:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}还没店里的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.89,0:26:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}吓我一跳 为什么在啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.90,0:26:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.77,0:26:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}你为什么在啊?等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.84,0:26:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么了?\N为什么?等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.78,0:26:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等\N你不接客吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.85,0:26:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}还没有客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.79,0:27:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等这是怎么回事?\NJULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.79,0:27:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}果然这个…不是在拍摄吗?\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.79,0:27:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天AV的果然不拍有这种情色的话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.80,0:27:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行吧?\N今天没有预约摄影棚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.81,0:27:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}什么?骗人?今天是1日店长的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.88,0:27:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}被拜托了啊 是 我们没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.78,0:28:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA不能出声哦\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.82,0:28:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.85,0:29:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}蹲下去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.87,0:29:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事吧?JULIA\N才不是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.81,0:29:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.76,0:29:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里有点。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.77,0:30:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.79,0:30:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA会被发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.86,0:30:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有放玩具啊\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.80,0:31:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}叫出声了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.88,0:31:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要忍住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行\N怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.70,0:32:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有客人...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.77,0:32:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.87,0:32:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这个不错\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.81,0:32:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没关系 因为JULIA是店长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.76,0:34:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}到下面来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.84,0:34:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}忍住声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.79,0:34:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.60,0:34:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}关掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.73,0:35:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}下面帮他关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很爽吗?\N很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.70,0:35:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事了回收银台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA...的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.85,0:35:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为是AV女优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.85,0:35:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我想应该是要做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.79,0:35:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能是那样 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}来了我会遮住的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.81,0:36:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快点 真的?\N快点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.84,0:36:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}发出声音的话会被发现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.78,0:36:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有人?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.72,0:37:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快遮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.77,0:37:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}刚有被看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.84,0:37:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.81,0:38:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.76,0:38:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA啊 真是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.77,0:39:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}完全不会厌恶\N因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.72,0:39:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}插入吧肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.80,0:39:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.80,0:39:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.88,0:39:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.84,0:40:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.76,0:40:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.84,0:41:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}safe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.84,0:41:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不要再做了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}回摄影棚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.78,0:41:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}看要去摄影棚还是要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.85,0:41:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事了\N不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.86,0:41:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有人啊\N都到这了没有停止的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.80,0:41:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}回摄影棚拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.80,0:41:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}现在是好机会\N不行啦 就在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.88,0:41:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.83,0:43:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是没人了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.83,0:43:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}后面后面\N在后面?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.77,0:43:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在后面吗?我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.85,0:43:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}回去吧\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.79,0:43:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.79,0:43:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.80,0:43:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经结束了\N现在是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.75,0:44:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有JULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.75,0:44:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA ...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.83,0:44:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA 这是JULIA的自慰套吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.72,0:44:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是真人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.86,0:45:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.83,0:45:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}店长
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.84,0:45:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}店长
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.88,0:46:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.82,0:46:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA后面...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.83,0:46:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是刚那个人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.77,0:46:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那个人?\N一直在看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.28,0:46:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.85,0:47:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没差了吧?\N没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.72,0:47:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}找到自慰套了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.72,0:47:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}找到自慰套了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.79,0:47:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}找到自慰套了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.80,0:47:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以的话请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.80,0:47:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.74,0:47:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.75,0:47:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}太怪了...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.89,0:47:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这个请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.76,0:47:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}卖了2个啊 卖了2各
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.77,0:47:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.78,0:47:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.78,0:48:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题啦 对业绩有贡献了 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.79,0:48:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA有人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.86,0:48:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不好意思现在正在拍摄AV
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.73,0:48:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请别在意不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.81,0:48:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}会在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.82,0:48:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那可以了JULIA什么可以了?叫出声的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.82,0:48:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}为什么?因为都被看到了可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.83,0:48:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}忍不住了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.86,0:49:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.73,0:49:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.76,0:49:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.83,0:50:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}流了好多汗不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.85,0:50:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA怎样?在这种地方做爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.78,0:50:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}开心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.79,0:50:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}店长啊 没生气的话 有什么关条
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.87,0:50:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}能有贡献吗?\N有贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.41,0:50:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.81,0:50:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}再多做点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.81,0:50:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以出声没关条吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.81,0:50:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}反正没客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.75,0:50:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.82,0:51:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}什么没关系啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.76,0:51:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可是这里..
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.83,0:51:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.80,0:51:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不热吗?\N有点热
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.91,0:52:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.76,0:53:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.83,0:53:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没这样做过 好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.80,0:54:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.84,0:54:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA 可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.85,0:54:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以射 射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.86,0:54:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}射在胸部上吗?\N射在胸部上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.86,0:54:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以射在胸部上?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.84,0:55:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.79,0:57:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快射了\N多射点
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.86,0:57:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.75,0:57:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害 射了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.85,0:58:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.73,0:58:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}嘴里也好多
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.87,0:58:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没听说这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.81,0:58:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}都忘了 这要怎办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.82,0:58:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}戴上去\N要戴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.82,0:58:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}店长...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.76,0:58:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}店长 不错啊 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.83,0:58:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这样对店有贡献吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.56,0:59:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不过卖了2个自慰套
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.42,0:59:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}卖了2个啊 还剩下1个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.84,0:59:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那...请男优买 男优...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.78,0:59:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是一样的吗?是不是一样的..
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.79,0:59:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那从酬劳扣可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.60,0:59:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不好意思 好贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.91,0:59:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA你买的话会很便宜吧?\N请试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.73,0:59:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请用原价买\N原价?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.51,0:59:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}卖完了3个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.27,0:59:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.80,0:59:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经够了这已经有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.87,0:59:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经不行了?够了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.81,0:59:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天就去摄影棚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.82,0:59:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}摄影棚？没有借
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.83,0:59:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}视野真好啊\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.83,1:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天天气好好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.85,1:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那JULIA\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.47,1:00:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.86,1:00:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的吗?\N因为这是规则啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.79,1:00:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}你抽了卡啊\N我抽了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.73,1:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那个...\N要全裸
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.48,1:00:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}乳交
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.74,1:00:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可是这里...会被看到哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.81,1:00:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里不妙吗?\N这里不妙啊 刚有人在看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.75,1:00:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的?那....
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.72,1:00:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这大楼的 再更没人烟的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.82,1:01:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不是那固问题
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.76,1:01:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}走吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.83,1:01:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在那边....
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.84,1:01:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}过来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.85,1:01:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里 我想不会有人来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.79,1:01:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}会有吧?\N欸?大概
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.79,1:01:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}结果不是跟刚一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.86,1:01:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不 可是 没问题啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.75,1:01:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.81,1:01:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}因为会有人来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.81,1:01:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA也不讨厌紧张刺激的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.75,1:01:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}或觉你好像有说过\N可是那个和这个不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.82,1:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在这种地方的不一样啊\N不一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.89,1:02:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不一样\N知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.76,1:02:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那啊...能请你脱衣服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.76,1:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的要脱?\N全部拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.40,1:02:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可是会没东西遮
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.50,1:02:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题 一边把风一边拍摄
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.78,1:02:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗? 外面不会有人来吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.78,1:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}来了再说
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.79,1:02:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.87,1:02:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}感觉已经习惯了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.87,1:02:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}请不要这样说
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.77,1:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?\N脱掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.78,1:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不会有人来吗?”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.85,1:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好像有声音
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.79,1:03:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那么衣服给我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.80,1:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好像有声音
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.80,1:03:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么办?衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.74,1:04:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}还给我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.88,1:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}安静的话就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.82,1:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那JULIA站超来 站起来立正
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.89,1:04:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.76,1:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}立正
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.70,1:04:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那请转一圈
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.86,1:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真棒的身材啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.79,1:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}现在不是说那个的时候\N不是那个时候?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.80,1:05:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很危险
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.87,1:05:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那JULIA...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.87,1:05:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可以吗?全裸的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.88,1:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}口交乳交
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.81,1:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}肉棒可以登场吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.82,1:05:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.83,1:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA请你蹲下
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.87,1:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?\N我想应该是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.79,1:07:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很紧张?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.86,1:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有人来了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.88,1:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在下面\N真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.89,1:07:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA 机会 机会
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.89,1:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是好机会
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.79,1:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题?\N现在没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.83,1:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有人来了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.84,1:09:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行啊 好可怕 停止吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.85,1:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}再一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.78,1:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不是那个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.82,1:09:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}住了挺多人的\N就是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.90,1:09:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.84,1:10:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}外面..
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.86,1:10:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不过看起来很爽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.81,1:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}肉棒在说好爽哦\N在说好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.82,1:10:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有在说吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.81,1:11:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}看起来真爽\N变硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.77,1:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}何时会来呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.80,1:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.81,1:12:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}射出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.84,1:13:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA的衣服到哪去了?\N到哪去了啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.79,1:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}到房间里来了\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.79,1:13:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}静不下来吗?\N不...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.87,1:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没问题吗?又想做什廖啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.87,1:14:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想做什么?\N又想做什廖吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.87,1:14:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有想做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.88,1:14:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}辛苦了 你看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.82,1:14:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是刚好来玩的\N刚好?你好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.76,1:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是这样啊\N刚刚 JULIA
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.89,1:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又请你抽卡了\N我没抽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.77,1:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}边打电话边OO的 抽了这张卡
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.77,1:14:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我没抽\N边打电话..?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.37,1:14:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}你干嘛说谎?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.71,1:14:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不懂要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.71,1:14:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}想说朦混过去的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.84,1:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}已经知道了吧?\N是 知道
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.78,1:14:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}从刚起。。。
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.79,1:14:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是朋友吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.79,1:14:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是吗?是男生?女生?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.86,1:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}女生\N是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.87,1:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}机会难得 电话的对象...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.80,1:15:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}能请你打给朋友吗?\N真的要打?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.74,1:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}对
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.88,1:15:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不论有什么事JULIA....\N不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.82,1:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那个没反应的话...\N没有接哦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.76,1:15:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没有接
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.97,1:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}喂 抱歉啊 刚刚
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.84,1:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.71,1:15:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.79,1:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.86,1:16:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.80,1:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的?是收讯不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.74,1:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我重打哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.81,1:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的 真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.89,1:16:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这个不行 真的 会很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.31,1:16:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}是你用奇怪的讲话方式啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.76,1:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不是的 因为他说收讯不好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.76,1:16:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}又打来了 怎么了?没事的只要JULIA
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.70,1:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没反应的话就是啊没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.84,1:16:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}....没问题的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.85,1:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不会再摸了  再一次\N真的吗? 是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.78,1:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那再一次
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.79,1:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}只打电话就没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.86,1:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}抱歉 好像收讯不好 大概没问题了
