Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.80,1:47:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.88,1:47:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.83,1:47:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.77,1:47:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.78,1:48:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.79,1:48:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.73,1:48:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.81,1:48:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.81,1:48:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.82,1:48:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}(讲电话)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.82,1:48:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我明天再打给你
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.83,1:48:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我再打给你哦那明天见
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.84,1:49:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.75,1:51:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.77,1:53:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}到晚上了啊\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.77,1:53:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这边人好多
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.84,1:53:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}人很多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.85,1:53:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}人很多的地方...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.85,1:53:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}今天都是去人多的地方\N很不安吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.86,1:53:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很不安..是AV吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.79,1:53:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}现在要去电影院\N太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.90,1:53:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好像很开心的样子\N因为要看电影啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.61,1:53:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里是电影院\N今天是上映什么片啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.80,1:54:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不知道 不看看的话\N不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.81,1:54:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不过是那个哦JULIA
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.81,1:54:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不只是单单去看电影而已
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.88,1:54:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我都忘了 对喔
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.75,1:54:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不过能看吧?\N看是能看
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.76,1:54:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}总之要去看看?\N好
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.86,1:55:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好久没来电影院了\N很久了?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.80,1:55:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不太看吗?\N不太看的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.74,1:55:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好像很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.81,1:55:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.82,1:55:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}电影也开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.89,1:55:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}...来开始吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.77,1:55:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在这里?真的?现在?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.77,1:55:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那拜诋了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.23,1:56:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.77,1:56:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.84,1:56:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}绝对不行出声哦\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.75,1:59:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.82,2:04:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA会被听见哦这样子
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.72,2:04:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}嘘
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.81,2:05:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.83,2:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}咕啾咕啾的
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.84,2:08:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}会被听见声音哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.77,2:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}这里真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.71,2:12:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}我后面有人
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.88,2:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}整只插进去了
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.83,2:15:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}那要不做吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:27.79,2:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:55.75,2:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}真的会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.82,2:22:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}先遮起来
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.73,2:22:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}己经不行 了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.88,2:25:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}JULIA...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.75,2:27:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好爽 快去了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.83,2:28:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}快射了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.77,2:29:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:12.78,2:30:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}在这种地方做爱了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.85,2:30:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.73,2:30:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.81,2:30:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}很爽
Dialogue: 0,2:30:46.81,2:30:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}咕啾咕啾的
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.82,2:30:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}骗人?因为兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:57.89,2:31:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}兴奋了吗?\N不能出声很难受
Dialogue: 0,2:31:04.83,2:31:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不过很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.83,2:31:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不能出声很兴奋吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:12.70,2:31:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能两边都有
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.78,2:31:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}你应该不讨厌这样的吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.78,2:31:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:31:29.79,2:31:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}可能会被抓\N可能会被抓啊
Dialogue: 0,2:31:36.73,2:31:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不是的
Dialogue: 0,2:31:40.87,2:31:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}没那回事?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:54.75,2:31:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}有很爽太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.82,2:32:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}第一次
Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.83,2:32:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}不赶快的话
Dialogue: 0,2:32:11.83,2:32:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKaiTi\fs12}内裤失踪了
